name: RELAY
description:
2021 has passed with mixed feelings. however, the feeling of sadness that dominates it. It is not easy to go through, there are many challenges and obstacles that stand in the way. I'm so grateful that I survived and got through it.

Now, the day has changed, the month has changed, and the year has changed. However, this self will never change, stay with the same spirit. Like a relay race, moving with a spirit stick in turns until we reach the finish line or the goal we have dreamed of.

Happy New Year!
